text: Nadia Conceição Almada (born 28 January 1977) is a Portuguese reality television star who lives in the United Kingdom.Researcha Almada became known in the UK after winning the fifth series of Big Brother UK. Since then, she has appeared on many TV shows (including a winners version of Big Brother). Almada also released a song in 2004. She is a transgender woman. == Sources == Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:British television personalities Category:Transgender women
